+## Performance Benchmarks
+
+### Expected Performance (Relative to Scalar)
+
+| Operation | Scalar | AVX2 | AVX-512 |
+|-----------|--------|------|---------|
+| Dot Product | 1x | 8-10x | 14-16x |
+| Conv 3x3 | 1x | 4-6x | 8-12x |
+| BatchNorm | 1x | 6-8x | 10-14x |
+| ReLU | 1x | 7-8x | 15-16x |
